collection.name: Acrocalypse
collection.description:
Acrocalypse is the ecosystem NFT for paperhands.gg. Your Croc isn’t only a PFP collectible that will take you on missions throughout the Acrocalypse galaxy, but the key that opens the door to next-generation digital utility, ✨ good vibes ✨, future mints and more. Buckle up, Crocs!
Head to https://claim.acrocalypse.gg to check if a croc has claimed it's $PAPER.
